synopsis: One day, walking down the street with his friend Mateo, Santiago stops to look at a church. In that brief moment, Santiago will have fantasies about a world where his friend is no longer; experiences nightmares and flashbacks of Mateo. But immediately, Mateo catches his attention, Santiago stops looking at the church, abandons his fantasy and continues walking alongside Mateo.
A rainy day in San Luis
tagline: wind, drops and water...lots of water

synopsis: After receiving a pair of the world's most advanced Virtual Reality headset, a young man finds himself transported to a city full of chaos and bedlam where he meets the world's most advanced A.I. trainer.
